(78, 'widget_text', 'a:5:{i:1;a:0:{}i:2;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:32:\"Welcome To Prima Foods Bulgaria!\";s:4:\"text\";s:434:\"We, at Prima Foods Bulgaria, aspire to provide quality processed chicken products. We strive to create one of the healthiest and nutritionist white meat products which will benefit children and adults alike. Our product line sells well as we have created products that are unique form other similar businesses. Our wide variety of chicken products are prepared with the most finest of ingredients which generates a distinctive flavor.\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:21:\"Unique in Our Own Way\";s:4:\"text\";s:826:\"Our chickens are raised on poultry farms and receive natural feed. Our suppliers allow them to freely roam on farmland, thus allowing the chicks to grow in a free and healthy environment that is clean from harmful chemicals and contaminants. Eventually, we are able to manufacture the best quality and healthiest white meat products available.\r\n\r\nOur product packaging is versatile and unique which prevents the products from going bad by serving well for storage purposes. We have built efficient cold storage units in our factories, where we store our processed meat until shipment time.\r\n\r\nOur facilities are BRC certified to meet food safety and quality standards along with being a halal producer of chicken products.\r\n\r\nOur goal is to serve consumers with one of the best quality and superior chicken products available.\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;}i:4;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:28:\"Thanks you for your feedback\";s:4:\"text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}', 'yes'),
