(146, 1, '2016-03-08 13:32:33', '2016-03-08 13:32:33', '<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong>Choose Prima Foods Bulgaria for Prime Chicken Products</strong></span>\n\nIn the year 1994, after intensive market research, strategic planning and relationship building, Prima Foods Bulgaria became a part of the global market of processed chicken products. Innovation and originality is our focal point. We pay close attention to procurement, processing and marketing of our chicken products. This is to ensure our customers do not only get superior taste, but healthy and nutritional chicken products as well.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Our Processed Chicken</strong></span>\n\nCurrently, Prima Foods Bulgaria has two mechanized processing facilities in Bulgaria. For each of these facilities, we have established a team of employees who are responsible for carefully manufacturing and preparing our line of processed chicken products. Our employees are thoroughly trained to preserve and maintain food quality standards. To ensure food safety, our quality control team inspects each step along the processing line.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Our Distribution System</strong>\n\nWe at Prima Foods Bulgaria, focus on delivering high quality, hygienic and healthy chicken products for you and your family. We supply our top notch chicken products not only in Bulgaria, but to our partners in Netherlands, UK, Germany, Denmark and Sweden as well. With the help of our international partners, we have maintained direct customer relationships. Our international relations are the key to our ongoing product innovation. This has made it easier for us to reach international markets and adapt to changing customer tastes.\n\nWe are privileged to be awarded international certifications for the practices which we have implemented in our factories.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>HACCP Certified</strong>\n\nPrima Foods SA guarantees production of food that is safe and free of biological plus chemical contamination. As we are following the guidelines outlined by HACCP (Hazard Analysis &amp; Critical Control Points), we have ensured our chicken products lie in the category of safe and superior quality food. This has made us a HACCAP Certified Company.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>BRC Global Standards</strong>\n\nWe feel honored to be a BRC Certified company. Prima Foods Bulgaria has been given this credit due to our compliance to BRC Global Standards. Our production lines are consistently clean and hygienic, so that our clients receive healthy hygienic food products. Under the BRC Standards, we have ensured our production process sustains its quality, safety, legal obligations and operational standards.\n\n<strong> </strong>\n\n<strong>Halal Certification</strong>\n\nOur business is one of the pioneers of manufacturing halal white meat products in Bulgaria, due to which we have earned the Halal Certification. Throughout our production process, we follow the Islamic teachings of slaughtering by hand and thorough cleaning. Our products are 100% halal and can be consumed by Muslims without worry.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-08 13:32:33', '2016-03-08 13:32:33', '', 14, 'http://prima.bg/14-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
